{"image_id": "KEY_2014_page_173", "image_size": [1275, 1650], "ocr": [{"text": "Education lending business. The discontinued education lending business consists of assets and liabilities", "bbox": [162.5, 158.9, 1056.0, 179.9]}, {"text": "(recorded at fair value) in the securitization trusts, as well as loans in portfolio (recorded at fair value), and loans", "bbox": [162.5, 184.1, 1102.5, 204.9]}, {"text": "in portfolio (recorded at carrying value with appropriate valuation reserves) that are outside the trusts. All of", "bbox": [162.5, 209.1, 1067.7, 229.9]}, {"text": "these loans were excluded from the table above as follows:", "bbox": [162.5, 234.1, 654.4, 254.9]}, {"text": "/ Loans at carrying value, net of allowance, of $2.1 billion ($1.8 billion at fair value) at December 31, 2014,", "bbox": [172.9, 265.1, 1093.2, 290.8]}, {"text": "and $2.4 billion ($2.0 billion at fair value) at December 31, 2013;", "bbox": [204.2, 295.0, 751.3, 315.8]}, {"text": "/ Portfolio loans at fair value of $191 million at December 31, 2014, and $147 million at December 31, 2013;", "bbox": [172.9, 326.0, 1105.4, 351.8]}, {"text": "and", "bbox": [204.2, 355.9, 234.3, 376.8]}, {"text": "/ Loans in the trusts at fair value of $2.0 billion at December 31, 2013.", "bbox": [172.9, 386.9, 781.5, 412.7]}, {"text": "Securities issued by the education lending securitization trusts, which are the primary liabilities of the trusts,", "bbox": [162.5, 438.9, 1067.8, 459.7]}, {"text": "totaling $1.8 billion in fair value at December 31, 2013, are also excluded from the above table.", "bbox": [162.5, 463.9, 961.1, 484.7]}, {"text": "These loans and securities are classified as Level 3 because we rely on unobservable inputs when determining", "bbox": [162.5, 510.8, 1080.3, 531.7]}, {"text": "fair value since observable market data is not available.", "bbox": [162.5, 535.8, 625.6, 556.7]}, {"text": "On September 30, 2014, we sold the residual interests in all of our outstanding education loan securitization", "bbox": [162.5, 582.8, 1063.0, 603.7]}, {"text": "trusts to a third party. With that transaction, in accordance with the applicable accounting guidance, we", "bbox": [162.5, 607.8, 1024.0, 628.7]}, {"text": "deconsolidated the securitization trusts and removed the trust assets and liabilities from our balance sheet at", "bbox": [162.5, 632.8, 1062.0, 653.7]}, {"text": "September 30, 2014. Additional information regarding the sale of the residual interests and deconsolidation of", "bbox": [162.5, 657.8, 1081.9, 678.7]}, {"text": "the securitization trusts is provided in Note 13 (“Acquisitions and Discontinued Operations”).", "bbox": [162.5, 682.8, 944.9, 703.7]}, {"text": "Residential real estate mortgage loans. Residential real estate mortgage loans with carrying amounts of $2.2", "bbox": [162.5, 729.6, 1079.1, 750.6]}, {"text": "billion at December 31, 2014, and December 31, 2013, are included in “Loans, net of allowance” in the previous", "bbox": [162.5, 754.8, 1102.7, 775.6]}, {"text": "table.", "bbox": [162.5, 779.8, 208.2, 800.6]}, {"text": "Short-term financial instruments. For financial instruments with a remaining average life to maturity of less", "bbox": [162.5, 826.6, 1078.8, 847.6]}, {"text": "than six months, carrying amounts were used as an approximation of fair values.", "bbox": [162.5, 851.8, 834.8, 872.6]}, {"text": "7. Securities", "bbox": [572.8, 921.5, 702.0, 946.5]}, {"text": "The amortized cost, unrealized gains and losses, and fair value of our securities available for sale and held-to-", "bbox": [162.5, 971.9, 1079.0, 992.7]}, {"text": "maturity securities are presented in the following table. Gross unrealized gains and losses represent the difference", "bbox": [162.5, 996.9, 1110.9, 1017.7]}, {"text": "between the amortized cost and the fair value of securities on the balance sheet as of the dates indicated.", "bbox": [162.5, 1021.9, 1032.5, 1042.7]}, {"text": "Accordingly, the amount of these gains and losses may change in the future as market conditions change. For", "bbox": [162.5, 1046.9, 1075.3, 1067.7]}, {"text": "more information about our securities available for sale and held-to-maturity securities and the related accounting", "bbox": [162.5, 1071.9, 1112.4, 1092.7]}, {"text": "policies, see Note 1 (“Summary of Significant Accounting Policies”).", "bbox": [162.5, 1096.9, 743.1, 1117.7]}, {"text": "2014", "bbox": [659.8, 1141.8, 684.8, 1154.3]}, {"text": "2013", "bbox": [960.2, 1141.8, 985.2, 1154.3]}, {"text": "December 31,", "bbox": [162.5, 1183.4, 235.3, 1195.9]}, {"text": "in millions", "bbox": [162.5, 1200.1, 215.6, 1212.6]}, {"text": "Amortized", "bbox": [532.5, 1183.4, 589.4, 1195.9]}, {"text": "Cost", "bbox": [565.0, 1200.1, 589.3, 1212.6]}, {"text": "Gross", "bbox": [637.2, 1166.8, 668.4, 1179.3]}, {"text": "Unrealized", "bbox": [610.2, 1183.4, 668.5, 1195.9]}, {"text": "Gains", "bbox": [637.2, 1200.1, 668.5, 1212.6]}, {"text": "Gross", "bbox": [716.2, 1166.8, 747.5, 1179.3]}, {"text": "Unrealized", "bbox": [689.3, 1183.4, 747.6, 1195.9]}, {"text": "Losses", "bbox": [712.7, 1200.1, 747.4, 1212.6]}, {"text": "Fair", "bbox": [789.3, 1183.4, 812.2, 1195.9]}, {"text": "Value", "bbox": [780.8, 1200.1, 812.1, 1212.6]}, {"text": "Amortized", "bbox": [832.9, 1183.4, 889.8, 1195.9]}, {"text": "Cost", "bbox": [865.4, 1200.1, 889.7, 1212.6]}, {"text": "Gross", "bbox": [937.6, 1166.8, 968.9, 1179.3]}, {"text": "Unrealized", "bbox": [910.6, 1183.4, 969.0, 1195.9]}, {"text": "Gains", "bbox": [937.6, 1200.1, 968.9, 1212.6]}, {"text": "Gross", "bbox": [1016.7, 1166.8, 1047.9, 1179.3]}, {"text": "Unrealized", "bbox": [989.7, 1183.4, 1048.0, 1195.9]}, {"text": "Losses", "bbox": [1013.1, 1200.1, 1047.9, 1212.6]}, {"text": "Fair", "bbox": [1089.7, 1183.4, 1112.6, 1195.9]}, {"text": "Value", "bbox": [1081.3, 1200.1, 1112.5, 1212.6]}, {"text": "SECURITIES AVAILABLE FOR SALE", "bbox": [162.5, 1223.0, 381.3, 1235.5]}, {"text": "States and political subdivisions", "bbox": [162.5, 1239.8, 322.9, 1252.